<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>Caesar to Stephanos, greetings.</p>
<p>You know my affection for my friend Zoilos. I have freed his native city and recommended it to Antonius</p>
<p>Since Antonius is absent, take care that no burden falls on them. This one city I have taken for mine out of all Asia. I wish these people to be protected as my own townsmen.</p>
<p>I will see that you carry out my recommendation to the full.</p>
</div>
